65
00:11:08,800 --> 00:11:11,239
Miss! I found it.

66
00:11:11,960 --> 00:11:14,100
Miss?

67
00:11:14,960 --> 00:11:16,560
Miss?

68
00:11:19,400 --> 00:11:20,759
Miss,

69
