Hurry up.

116
00:17:52,840 --> 00:17:54,440
What's the matter?

117
00:18:43,400 --> 00:18:46,480
Shi Li. Shi Li.

118
00:18:46,480 --> 00:18:48,020
Your Highness?

119
00:18:54,240 --> 00:18:55,520
Your Highness,

120
00:18:55,520 --> 00:18:57,120
