141
00:22:48,420 --> 00:22:50,920
then I'll die in one hit.

142
00:22:50,920 --> 00:22:55,959
Otherwise, she'll ask me to catch more venomous bugs

143
00:22:55,959 --> 00:22:57,959
until she can master that technique.

144
00:22:57,960 --> 00:23:00,300
I will die either way.

145
00:23:00,300 --> 00:23:03,060
So why should I head back?

146
00:23:26,280 --> 00:23:27,980
Young Master.

147
00:23:29,680 --> 00:23:33,480
Intelligent Gentleman sent his envoy here to deliver us an invitation.

148
00:23:34,540 --> 00:23:37,420
Intelligent Gentleman, Su Xinghe?

149
00:23:38,120 --> 00:23:39,720
What for?

150
00:23:42,720 --> 00:23:48,819
"I, Su Xinghe, courteously invite all chess aficionados to gather together

151
00:23:48,819 --> 00:23:53,820
at the Soundless Canyon by Leigu Mountain, Henan on the 8th of February.

152
00:23:53,820 --> 00:23:55,920
I await your presence."

153
00:23:57,800 --> 00:24:02,460
What do all of you think?

154
00:24:03,400 --> 00:24:06,740
