00:31:52,780 --> 00:31:56,519
Who knew that it's just a vanity name

260
00:31:56,519 --> 00:31:58,880
because you can't even get out of a fish net.

261
00:31:58,880 --> 00:32:00,980
Since Xingxiu Sect loves poison that much,

262
00:32:00,980 --> 00:32:04,880
let's dig all their poison out and make them ingest it.

263
00:32:04,880 --> 00:32:06,939
Let's rid the martial world of its pest.

264
00:32:06,939 --> 00:32:09,040
Yes!

265
00:32:09,040 --> 00:32:11,339
Almighty Beggars' Sect! Release me, please.

266
00:32:11,339 --> 00:32:12,999
I will offer you a huge favor.

267
00:32:13,000 --> 00:32:14,600
Release you?

268
00:32:14,600 --> 00:32:15,999
What good will I get out of it?

269
00:32:15,999 --> 00:32:18,180
Xingxiu Sect has three treasures.

270
00:32:18,180 --> 00:32:20,999
Only Old Freak of Xingxiu and I know where they are.

271
00:32:21,000 --> 00:32:22,319
Spare my life.

272
00:32:22,320 --> 00:32:27,000
Once you kill Old Freak of Xingxiu, I'll hand those treasures to you.

273
00:32:27,000 --> 00:32:28,999
Don't be fooled, hero.

274
00:32:29,000 --> 00:32:31,700
One of the treasures was stolen long ago.

275
00:32:31,700 --> 00:32:33,020
You should release me.

276
00:32:33,020 --> 00:32:35,839
Only I'm the one who's loyal to you.

277
00:32:35,839 --> 00:32:36,840
Disgusting.

278
00:32:36,840 --> 00:32:39,039
Hero, hero. Don't listen to them.

279
00:32:39,039 --> 00:32:40,660
They are all liars.

280
00:32:40,660 --> 00:32:42,260
Release me.

281
00:32:42,260 --> 00:32:45,259
I'm the most loyal one.

282
00:32:45,259 --> 00:32:48,500
Sir, I know most of Xingxiu Sect's techniques.

283
00:32:48,500 --> 00:32:50,640
I will share them with you.

284
00:32:50,640 --> 00:32:52,660
All of them.

285
00:32:52,660 --> 00:32:54,840
Hero!

286
00:32:54,840 --> 00:32:56,800
You guys...

287
00:32:56,800 --> 00:32:59,480
You betrayed your Master so easily.

288
00:32:59,480 --> 00:33:01,220
How could you swear loyalty to another person?

289
00:33:01,220 --> 00:33:03,760
What a joke!

290
00:33:03,760 --> 00:33:05,559
Old Freak of Xingxiu is a weakling.

291
00:33:05,560 --> 00:33:08,740
Being loyal to him won't do me any good.

292
00:33:08,740 --> 00:33:11,559
But the power of Beggars' Sect travels far and wide.

293
00:33:11,560 --> 00:33:14,920
Old Freak of Xingxiu can never hold a candle to it.

294
00:33:14,920 --> 00:33:17,079
The word "hero" is not enough to depict your prowess.

295
00:33:17,080 --> 00:33:18,879
You should be called a martial saint.

296
00:33:18,880 --> 00:33:22,239
I'm good with words. I can help to promote your name.

297
00:33:22,240 --> 00:33:25,180
That way, everyone will know your sect.

298
00:33:25,180 --> 00:33:27,780
The heroism of Beggars' Sect is common knowledge now.

299
00:33:27,780 --> 00:33:29,239
They don't need you to promote it.

300
00:33:29,240 --> 00:33:32,979
I'm the first to call you a saint and a savior.

301
00:33:32,979 --> 00:33:37,140
The others only know to echo after me. They have no contributions.

302
00:33:37,140 --> 00:33:39,259
I don't understand why Old Freak of Xingxiu

303
00:33:39,259 --> 00:33:42,360
would keep groveling scoundrels as his disciples.

304
00:33:42,360 --> 00:33:44,940
Let me kill you first, Old Freak of Xingxiu.

305
00:33:44,940 --> 00:33:47,319
And the others will follow suit.

306
00:33:47,320 --> 00:33:50,140
No need.

307
00:33:50,140 --> 00:33:53,400
Don't stop.

308
00:34:03,760 --> 00:34:05,760
Are you okay?

309
00:34:21,700 --> 00:34:24,119
Back off. They are poisonous.

310
00:34:40,159 --> 00:34:42,740
Oh no! I've been poisoned.

311
00:34:44,480 --> 00:34:46,280
Retreat.

312
00:34:46,280 --> 00:34:48,279
- Retreat now!
- Stay here.

313
00:34:48,279 --> 00:34:50,939
Stay here. You guys are not all poisoned yet.

314
00:34:50,939 --> 00:34:52,158
I...

315
00:34:52,159 --> 00:34:54,399
Come back and release us!

316
00:34:54,399 --> 00:34:58,520
Old Deity of Xingxiu managed to turn the table.

317
00:34:58,520 --> 00:35:00,779
Impressive.

318
00:35:00,779 --> 00:35:05,779
If he catches me here, I'll die.

319
00:35:15,160 --> 00:35:18,240
Master! Your technique is unrivaled

320
00:35:18,240 --> 00:35:22,999
Before we know it, the panhandlers fled with tails between their legs.

321
00:35:22,999 --> 00:35:24,199
Don't listen to him, Master.

322
00:35:24,200 --> 00:35:28,679
He was the one who called those panhandlers a saint and a savior.

323
00:35:28,679 --> 00:35:30,279
I followed Master for several years.

324
00:35:30,279 --> 00:35:32,779
Of course, I know Master is omnipotent.

325
00:35:32,779 --> 00:35:36,739
I was just coddling the panhandlers so that they let their guard down

326
00:35:36,739 --> 00:35:39,579
and Master could use his marvelous technique.

327
00:35:39,579 --> 00:35:42,399
It's all my fault, Master. I was dumb.

328
00:35:42,399 --> 00:35:45,459
I shouldn't have surrendered. I regret it very much.

329
00:35:45,459 --> 00:35:47,519
I'd rather die in the hands of the panhandlers

330
00:35:47,519 --> 00:35:49,679
than beg for your forgiveness again, Master.

331
00:35:49,680 --> 00:35:54,079
Forgive us, Master.

332
00:35:54,079 --> 00:35:55,680
All right. All right.

333
00:35:55,680 --> 00:36:00,160
Whoever frees me will be able to live.

334
00:36:00,160 --> 00:36:02,879
But no blade can cut through this net.

335
00:36:02,879 --> 00:36:04,819
If someone can undo the knot there,

336
00:36:04,819 --> 00:36:06,559
then we can get out of the net.

337
00:36:06,559 --> 00:36:10,540
We're in the middle of nowhere. No one can help us.

338
00:36:11,240 --> 00:36:14,340
They can't possibly send a clone to harm me.

339
00:36:14,340 --> 00:36:17,040
Now's the best time to flee.

340
00:36:19,000 --> 00:36:21,000
Mister! Kind soul!

341
00:36:21,000 --> 00:36:22,719
If you can free me from this net,

342
00:36:22,719 --> 00:36:25,180
I'll give you 1,000 taels.

343
00:36:25,180 --> 00:36:27,239
1,000 is not enough. 10,000 taels at least.

344
00:36:27,240 --> 00:36:29,240
10,000 taels!

345
00:36:29,240 --> 00:36:31,740
Mister, I know you are a righteous man.

346
00:36:31,740 --> 00:36:33,499
You will help us, won't you?

347
00:36:33,499 --> 00:36:36,419
- Save us, please.
- Save a soul to accumulate merits!

348
00:36:36,419 --> 00:36:38,439
Just untie the knot.

349
00:36:38,440 --> 00:36:39,919
There's no danger involved.

350
00:36:39,920 --> 00:36:42,359
Once we're free, we'll regard you as our savior.

351
00:36:42,359 --> 00:36:43,959
We will make one longevity tablet for you

352
00:36:43,960 --> 00:36:47,240
and we'll offer you incense and candles every day.

353
00:36:47,240 --> 00:36:49,740
Save us, kind Samaritan.

354
00:36:49,740 --> 00:36:51,399
Save us!

355
00:36:51,400 --> 00:36:53,679
Save us, please.

356
00:36:53,679 --> 00:36:55,919
Savior!

357
00:36:55,920 --> 00:36:57,439
Save us, kind Samaritan.

358
00:36:57,440 --> 00:36:58,719
I beg of you.

359
00:36:58,720 --> 00:36:59,839
Please.

360
00:36:59,840 --> 00:37:01,159
Save us, kind soul.

361
00:37:01,160 --> 00:37:02,679
Save us, hero.

362
00:37:02,680 --> 00:37:06,780
- Save us.
- 10,000 taels!

363
00:37:06,780 --> 00:37:08,799
Help us, please.

364
00:37:08,800 --> 00:37:10,159
Free me, mister.

365
00:37:10,160 --> 00:37:11,719
Help us, please.

366
00:37:11,720 --> 00:37:13,719
Free us.

367
00:37:13,720 --> 00:37:16,080
Help.

368
00:37:18,880 --> 00:37:25,260
Thanks, kind Samaritan.

369
00:37:25,260 --> 00:37:28,579
Us too! Help!

370
00:37:28,579 --> 00:37:32,400
Us too!

371
00:37:32,400 --> 00:37:35,720
Thank you, savior.

372
00:37:35,720 --> 00:37:37,719
Thanks.

373
00:37:37,719 --> 00:37:38,839
Let's go.

374
00:37:38,840 --> 00:37:42,140
Young man with an iron helmet. What's your name?

375
00:37:42,140 --> 00:37:45,020
I'm You Tanzhi.

376
00:37:46,000 --> 00:37:48,060
You Tanzhi.

377
00:37:48,060 --> 00:37:49,780
Great.

378
00:37:49,780 --> 00:37:54,419
Check those panhandlers and see if they are still breathing.

379
00:38:17,820 --> 00:38:22,739
Mister, they are all dead. You're so powerful.

380
00:38:24,560 --> 00:38:29,540
You're quite resistant to poison, too.

381
00:38:29,540 --> 00:38:31,440
Me?

382
00:38:31,980 --> 00:38:34,920
What poison resistance?

383
00:38:46,160 --> 00:38:48,840
You dare to kill my disciple?

384
00:38:51,640 --> 00:38:53,580
The audacity!

385
00:38:53,580 --> 00:38:55,940
Who's your master?

386
00:38:55,940 --> 00:38:58,319
I don't have a master, mister.

387
00:38:58,319 --> 00:39:00,700
I don't dare to kill your disciple, either.

388
00:39:12,040 --> 00:39:14,199
Spare my life, sir.

389
00:39:14,200 --> 00:39:16,100
Spare my life.

390
00:39:16,800 --> 00:39:21,539
I wonder if your plea is sincere or fake.

391
00:39:21,539 --> 00:39:23,539
It's very sincere, sir.

392
00:39:23,539 --> 00:39:25,359
Please spare my life.

393
00:39:25,359 --> 00:39:27,940
Spare you?

394
00:39:27,940 --> 00:39:30,919
Unless you become my disciple,

395
00:39:30,919 --> 00:39:33,940
or else, why should I spare you?

396
00:39:33,940 --> 00:39:36,600
I, You Tanzhi, wish to study under you.

397
00:39:36,600 --> 00:39:38,780
Please take me in, Master.

398
00:39:44,180 --> 00:39:47,060
Good.

399
00:39:47,060 --> 00:39:48,479
I have a question.

400
00:39:48,480 --> 00:39:50,799
Where did you learn martial arts?

401
00:39:50,799 --> 00:39:54,239
Where did you get your poison from?

402
00:39:54,239 --> 00:39:57,459
Master, I was a farm boy

403
00:39:57,459 --> 00:39:59,399
but the Liao invaded and took me away.

404
00:39:59,400 --> 00:40:01,160
I was forced to wear this helmet.

405
00:40:01,160 --> 00:40:02,819
I do not know any martial arts.

406
00:40:02,819 --> 00:40:06,560
However, one day, I went to the mountain

407
00:40:06,560 --> 00:40:11,679
and I was bitten by an ice silkworm that belonged to a monk called Hui Jing.

408
00:40:11,679 --> 00:40:14,379
My body was frozen solid and I almost died.

409
00:40:14,379 --> 00:40:17,659
When I woke up, the silkworm already died.

410
00:40:17,659 --> 00:40:19,239
What did the ice silkworm look like?

411
00:40:19,239 --> 00:40:22,519
Just like a normal silkworm

412
00:40:22,519 --> 00:40:24,079
but slightly bigger.

413
00:40:24,080 --> 00:40:29,539
A magical creature like this was somehow absorbed by your body.

414
00:40:29,539 --> 00:40:32,420
What a waste.

415
00:40:35,340 --> 00:40:40,500
If Monk Hui Jing can find an ice silkworm,

416
00:40:40,500 --> 00:40:43,900
he can find a second one,

417
00:40:43,900 --> 00:40:46,520
a third one.

418
00:40:49,020 --> 00:40:51,720
- You Tanzhi.
- Yes.

419
00:40:51,720 --> 00:40:55,500
Follow me to the mountain and find that monk, Hui Jing.

420
00:40:55,500 --> 00:40:57,300
Yes.

421
00:40:59,000 --> 00:41:02,460
We should arrive within half a day.

422
00:41:02,460 --> 00:41:05,960
Our young master must have departed already.

423
00:41:07,460 --> 00:41:09,919
This will be a dangerous trip.

424
00:41:09,919 --> 00:41:13,100
Everyone, stay alert.

425
00:41:13,860 --> 00:41:15,800
Amitabha.

426
00:41:15,800 --> 00:41:18,140
Misters, I came down from the mountain

427
00:41:18,140 --> 00:41:21,579
